      "id": "M1029",
      "name": "Remote Data Storage",
      "description": "Consider implementing IT disaster recovery plans that contain procedures for taking regular data backups that can be used to restore organizational data.[4] Ensure backups are stored off system and are protected from common methods adversaries may use to gain access and manipulate backups."
